            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Speratus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiae</ex></expan> ex b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciario</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>eli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>V</abbr><ex>iminacii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>I <expan><abbr>Aquet</abbr><ex>anorum</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ixit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nnos</ex></expan> LV <expan><abbr><am><g type="obitus"/></am></abbr><ex>obitus</ex></expan> in <expan><abbr>Britt</abbr><ex>annia</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Lucia Afrodisia con<lb break="no" n="7"/>iugi <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan> et sibi vivae <lb n="8"/>posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Aus 3 Fragmenten zusammengesetzt. Mehrere Reliefs: unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes Europa mit dem Stier zwischen den beiden Dioskuren; oberhalb der Inschrift Fries mit Jagdszene, darüber Raub der Persephone. (B): CIL III, ILS: Z. 1: nicht gelesen; Brunšmid, AE 1901, CIL III, ILS: Z. 5: Aq(itanorum) vet(eranae); AE 1901: Z. 5 (Ende): Br(i)t(tannia); CIL III: Z. 6/7: coniuci; ILS: Z. 6/7: con/iu[g]i.</p>
            </div>
